          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article01\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\t<mbr-parameters>\n\t\t<header>Size</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Content Width\" name=\"contentWidth\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"12\">\n\t\t<header>Show/Hide</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Card Bg\" name=\"wrapBgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n\t\t<header>Images</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"autoSize\" title=\"Auto Size\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" name=\"imageHeight\" title=\"Height\" min=\"1\" max=\"5\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\" condition=\"autoSize\">\n\t\t<header>Background</header>\n\t\t<fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#edefeb\" selected>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n\t\t</fieldset>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Transparent\" name=\"transparentBg\" condition=\"bg.type === 'color'\" checked>\n\t\t<header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.3\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t</mbr-parameters>\n\n\t<div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n\t<div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\"></div>\n\t<div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"card col-md-12 col-lg-{{contentWidth}}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"image-wrapper col-12 col-sm-6 justify-content-center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/3d78cc93-e9a0-43a8-ace5-19e746781acf-1256x837.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"image-wrapper col-12 col-sm-6 justify-content-center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/8c2b2f47-0998-4c65-baca-58ba0c3519db-1256x837.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box align-left mb-3 card-content-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style mbr-white mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .card-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>SiMoEns: Moldando futuros</b></h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3 mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Na SiMoEns, somos movidos pela&nbsp; inovação em tecnologia. Criamos experiências digitais que inspiram o aprendizado e a compreensão.....?</p>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3 mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Nossa história está enraizada em um compromisso com a excelência, constantemente expandindo os limites do que é possível na criação e simulação digital para servir à comunidade educacional.....?</p>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3 mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Acreditamos no poder da narrativa visual e da tecnologia interativa para tornar assuntos complexos acessíveis e envolventes para alunos de todas as idades????</p>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3 mb-0\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Read More</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</section>",
